    "information_content_info_9Ymtee": {
      "type": "information-content-info",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_hXcgxz": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Astrology, along with zodiac signs, lays strong emphasis on chakras. Chakras are centres of energy in the body that control our emotional, physical, and spiritual well-being. Gemstone jewelry and certain crystals play a really big role in chakra healing, chakra balancing, and chakra energy healing. Just as every gemstone’s frequency and vibrations resonate with cosmic bodies and energies, these frequencies are also believed to resonate with different chakras of our energy systems:</p><ul><li>Root Chakra (Muladhara): Red gemstones like Red Coral and Garnet bring necessary grounding and security. </li><li>Sacral Chakra (Swadhisthana): Carnelian is considered to encourage creativity and passion.</li><li>Solar Plexus Chakra (Manipura): Yellow Sapphires and Citrines are believed to enhance confidence and willpower. </li><li>Heart Chakra (Anahata): Emerald and Rose Quartz, in many cultures, are believed to enhance love and compassion.</li><li>Throat Chakra (Vishuddha): Aquamarine and Blue Topaz are considered to strengthen communication. </li><li>Third Eye Chakra (Ajna): Amethyst are widely considered to boost intuition and insight. </li><li>Crown Chakra (Sahasrara): Diamond or Clear Quartz brings spiritual clarity. </li></ul><p>Astrological rings, gemstone pendants, and zodiac sign pendants with the right gemstones are believed to restore balance and release blocked energy, aligning your chakras and delivering healing and amplification on a spiritual level. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_hXcgxz"
      ],
      "name": "Information Content",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": false,
        "show_on_homepage": false
      }
    },
    "information_content_info_UjGwaA": {
      "type": "information-content-info",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Fww8Ry": {
          "type": "heading",
          "name": "Role of Platinum in Astrology",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Role of Platinum in Astrology",
            "heading_level": "h2",
            "heading_id": "platinum",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "richtext_QXTzcc": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gold and silver have long been worshipped as metals of astrology and planetary energy. Gold (सोना) is associated with the Sun, which signifies vitality, triumph, and the nature of a leader; silver (चांदी) is associated with the Moon, encompassing peace, calm, and emotional wellness. That is why many classical 'remedies' recommended in astrology involve wearing gemstones in gold or silver.</p><p>But what about platinum jewelry? Platinum is relatively modern in discovery to Indian culture, and it is not mentioned in the ancient Vedic texts in terms of planetary association. However, currently, platinum is considered an astrological metal due to its properties.</p><p>While gold and silver make classic choices, platinum is now increasingly being referred to as a modern-day astrological metal. Because of the neutral property of platinum that has durability and planet association elements of Saturn and Venus, it is favourable for certain gemstones. If a Blue Sapphire (नीलम), Diamond (हीरा), or Cat's Eye (लहसुनिया) are one you are exploring, you can feel confident that if you set it in platinum, it will be functioning optimally and you have a piece of contemporary jewelry that you will feel proud to wear daily!</p><p>In Indian culture, jewelry and astrology signify a sacred, lasting bond. In terms of jewelry, from zodiac jewelry like aries necklaces and leo star sign jewelry to astrological rings, pendant jewelry, and gemstone earrings, every piece can serve a \"greater purpose\". When it comes to wearing jewelry, such as birthstone or zodiac jewelry chosen with the help of astrology, you are wearing jewelry that can provide protection, empowerment, and harmony.</p><p>Whether through chakra healing, getting aligned with an astrological gemstone that supports your spirit, or simply donning your sun sign pendant, appropriate jewelry guarantees you wear more than just the latest fashion… You wear cosmic balance.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Fww8Ry",
        "richtext_QXTzcc"
      ],
      "name": "Role of Platinum in Astrology",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": false,
        "show_on_homepage": false
      }
    },
