    "faq_section_K8NRXb": {
      "type": "faq-section",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_8GxLbB": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Can I wear a lab grown diamond for astrology purposes?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Can I wear a Lab Grown Diamond for astrology purposes?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Usually, astrologers recommend natural diamonds as they are believed to carry cosmic vibrations due to their natural origins and while lab grown diamonds are chemically and visually identical, they may not carry similar astrological energies.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_zQibDp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Can I wear a diamond for my rashi?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Can I wear a diamond for my rashi?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Diamonds are generally suitable for Aries Signs but if your astrologer prescribes it, you can wear it. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_qL9eEk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which shape of diamond is best for astrology?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which shape of diamond is best for astrology?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Round and oval cuts are believed to distribute the cosmic energies evenly and hence are the most recommended cuts for astrological diamond jewelry.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_iWi3t4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which stone is suitable for Vrishabha Rashi?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which stone is suitable for Vrishabha Rashi?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Emeralds and diamonds are the most suitable gemstones for the Vrishabha Rashi (Taurus).</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_U9T8g3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which nakshatra should wear gold?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which nakshatra should wear gold?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>People born under solar-influenced nakshatras (Example - Kritika or Uttara Phalguni) are usually advised to wear gold.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_ziV4Kc": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which stone suits me by date of birth?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which stone suits me by date of birth?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Astrologically, the gemstone that suits you best depends on your birth date and zodiac sign. The following gemstones are the most suited for their zodiac signs:</p><ol><li>Aries: Diamonds</li><li>Pisces: Aquamarine</li><li>Aquarius: Amethyst</li><li>Capricorn: Garnet</li><li>Sagittarius: Turquoise</li><li>Scorpio: Topaz</li><li>Libra: Opal</li><li>Virgo: Sapphire</li><li>Leo: Peridot</li><li>Gemini: Pearl</li><li>Cancer: Ruby</li><li>Taurus: Emerald</li></ol><p>To learn more, you can also consult a Vedic astrologer.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_hwQKtc": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Can Aries wear lab-grown diamonds?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Can Aries wear lab-grown diamonds?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Yes, a rose gold ring with lab grown diamonds will definitely complement an Aries’ courageous and passionate nature while aligning astrologically with Mars. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_TirBYW": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which is the most powerful stone to wear?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which is the most powerful stone to wear?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>While the power of the stone varies depending on the horoscope and birthchart, blue sapphires and diamonds are widely considered to be the most powerful gemstones. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PCGRz9": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "Which birthstone is the best?",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "Which birthstone is the best?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>There is no “one best gemstone” for everyone. The best gemstone is the one that helps you in different aspects of your life and is aligned with your astrological sign, sun sign, and cosmic requirements.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
